{"tid":684064,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"data science 學習 TG 谷s","createTime":"2018-05-30T08:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T10:28:50.000Z","uid":85029,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"41ed741a6f98675a3b9308d42731a2b588efa29d","tid":684064,"uid":85029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"有感香港無乜人提 DS (data science), 特別左呢幾個谷，希望大家有意學習Ching 和 sis 加入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/DS_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDS_hk&d=MFFHEQWs%2FHKsaOFf84186TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a6827804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/DS_hk</a> <br />\ndata science 資源組，綜合（主要英文）小量中文網路 有關 DS 既資源<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/R_datascience_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FR_datascience_hk&d=MFFHEQWs%2FHKsaOFf84186TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f7837726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/R_datascience_hk</a><br />\nR 是比較新的 數據分析專門語言，同 SAS/SPSS 同類，如果要深入研究 DS，學一門深入研究既語言基本系必須。這個谷專門討論和學習 R 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/pythondatascience_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpythondatascience_hk&d=MFFHEQWs%2FHKsaOFf84186TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d6b572e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/pythondatascience_hk</a><br />\nPython 是一款general language, 有本身的 data analysis library, 也有很多人採用 。這個谷主要討論 Python DS library 既應用。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家喜歡。"},{"pid":"20fd35b42e10e345f0a7643c00fc9b1d6dead67d","tid":684064,"uid":40684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"咩背景人多?"},{"pid":"07b887ddab2ccd8f194127b0bc693c1f6d9b4aab","tid":684064,"uid":85029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20fd35b42e10e345f0a7643c00fc9b1d6dead67d","tid":684064,"uid":40684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"咩背景人多?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"好問題， 乜 Background 都有， 反正對這個 Topic 有興趣